reviews.review_text:
As Any Good Deadhead Would Say: 
"Get it."

This is a superior matrix of an intensely gorgeous show. I was there that night and left the venue speechless. I had the World to Give. 

It was not my own. It was not mine to own, but I got it anyway.

And I try and I try and I try to give it away.

This is another one of those unheralded Jerry extravaganzas that defies explanation. He really came out of his shell blazing and blasted us big time. This recording sort of captures the dynamic in Winterland that night. Oh, heck, you just had to be there, but here you are.

49 out of 5 stars
